{"tid":349602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肥婆減肥post","createTime":"2017-08-06T15:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T17:32:55.000Z","uid":133957,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87d995b6eec0730fde8c6df443b416a18374a679","tid":349602,"uid":133957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"一拍拖就開始肥<br />\n依家肥到hihi<br />\n決心減肥<br />\n開post提自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2291a65b18258fe1e481dc1cc9f3de1545188a","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你情況一樣 所以特登set啲美極肥婆相做icon同wallpaper提自己"},{"pid":"c307e77de297e98cb133c542cd511771ad7f69f3","tid":349602,"uid":133957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:14:13.000Z","msg":"巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb185b7ba1b8551b7c20ab5beeb0cd8d1ecd384a","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係網上睇番尼 又真係work<br />\n飲食方面 早午晚餐順序咁減少份量，除左三餐之外下午茶可加餐<br />\n食啲低脂乳酪啲frd 唔洗話特登食少野，消耗量大過攝入既熱量就得（我係用app計）<br />\n<br />\n運動我就唔敢懶，開頭就跟YouTube有條片分享減肥話早午晚做三次唔同運動 但太chur ，改為一得閒/放假就跑步踩單車同plank 一星期三四次倒<br />\n如果你話唔想做太激烈 咁做啲修身既plank都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n我揀左自己覺得舒服既方法，唔一定要下下跟足人地<br />\n之前56-57kg 而家就52-53kg <br />\n唔想做肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 絲"},{"pid":"278c499d68077791393eb6dcdf04c6a688353e98","tid":349602,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你情況一樣 所以特登set啲美極肥婆相做icon同wallpaper提自己</blockquote><br />\n求wallpaper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ee9f7240f82c1fa92b207391824b7a976d5175","tid":349602,"uid":133957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係網上睇番尼 又真係work<br />\n飲食方面 早午晚餐順序咁減少份量，除左三餐之外下午茶可加餐<br />\n食啲低脂乳酪啲frd 唔洗話特登食少野，消耗量大過攝入既熱量就得（我係用app計）<br />\n<br />\n運動我就唔敢懶，開頭就跟YouTube有條片分享減肥話早午晚做三次唔同運動 但太chur ，改為一得閒/放假就跑步踩單車同plank 一星期三四次倒<br />\n如果你話唔想做太激烈 咁做啲修身既plank都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n我揀左自己覺得舒服既方法，唔一定要下下跟足人地<br />\n之前56-57kg 而家就52-53kg <br />\n唔想做肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打減左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我肥你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要減5kg"},{"pid":"06daab3ea87093f545fb9001287ef734f786556d","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你情況一樣 所以特登set啲美極肥婆相做icon同wallpaper提自己</blockquote><br />\n求wallpaper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/010838_9f0195c4a75c5605426df8108ba8d848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F010838_9f0195c4a75c5605426df8108ba8d848.jpg&h=b893a32c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/010839_7e388a7036926aba76b72167cfc68e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F010839_7e388a7036926aba76b72167cfc68e5d.jpg&h=07543f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/010840_7e388a7036926aba76b72167cfc68e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F010840_7e388a7036926aba76b72167cfc68e5d.jpg&h=1375a18e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/010841_b4d2af0bd4a6eb24323b051b8a046818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F010841_b4d2af0bd4a6eb24323b051b8a046818.jpg&h=6afeb7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ac598e47d8f433a077a3c375ad8b5e0a0b0fd3","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係網上睇番尼 又真係work<br />\n飲食方面 早午晚餐順序咁減少份量，除左三餐之外下午茶可加餐<br />\n食啲低脂乳酪啲frd 唔洗話特登食少野，消耗量大過攝入既熱量就得（我係用app計）<br />\n<br />\n運動我就唔敢懶，開頭就跟YouTube有條片分享減肥話早午晚做三次唔同運動 但太chur ，改為一得閒/放假就跑步踩單車同plank 一星期三四次倒<br />\n如果你話唔想做太激烈 咁做啲修身既plank都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n我揀左自己覺得舒服既方法，唔一定要下下跟足人地<br />\n之前56-57kg 而家就52-53kg <br />\n唔想做肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打減左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我肥你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要減5kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大概三四個月倒 但都唔係連續 仲繼左一排 所以減得算慢 （應該係）加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d71cbff8416d06ca0826f4dce86aba490b9955c","tid":349602,"uid":54685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係網上睇番尼 又真係work<br />\n飲食方面 早午晚餐順序咁減少份量，除左三餐之外下午茶可加餐<br />\n食啲低脂乳酪啲frd 唔洗話特登食少野，消耗量大過攝入既熱量就得（我係用app計）<br />\n<br />\n運動我就唔敢懶，開頭就跟YouTube有條片分享減肥話早午晚做三次唔同運動 但太chur ，改為一得閒/放假就跑步踩單車同plank 一星期三四次倒<br />\n如果你話唔想做太激烈 咁做啲修身既plank都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n我揀左自己覺得舒服既方法，唔一定要下下跟足人地<br />\n之前56-57kg 而家就52-53kg <br />\n唔想做肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用咩app計，因為唔太識用，好多時出街食左某啲野唔知點打返落去計<br />\n利申 絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打減左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我肥你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要減5kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大概三四個月倒 但都唔係連續 仲繼左一排 所以減得算慢 （應該係）加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48ac4520dd19709cde6d56c9025dac0b36ceae30","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係網上睇番尼 又真係work<br />\n飲食方面 早午晚餐順序咁減少份量，除左三餐之外下午茶可加餐<br />\n食啲低脂乳酪啲frd 唔洗話特登食少野，消耗量大過攝入既熱量就得（我係用app計）<br />\n<br />\n運動我就唔敢懶，開頭就跟YouTube有條片分享減肥話早午晚做三次唔同運動 但太chur ，改為一得閒/放假就跑步踩單車同plank 一星期三四次倒<br />\n如果你話唔想做太激烈 咁做啲修身既plank都應該夠<br />\n<br />\n我揀左自己覺得舒服既方法，唔一定要下下跟足人地<br />\n之前56-57kg 而家就52-53kg <br />\n唔想做肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用咩app計，因為唔太識用，好多時出街食左某啲野唔知點打返落去計<br />\n利申 絲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打減左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我肥你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼要減5kg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大概三四個月倒 但都唔係連續 仲繼左一排 所以減得算慢 （應該係）加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我用app大概分兩個用途<br />\n1）計食物卡路里 （[url]Calorie Mama AI : Food Photo Recognition &amp; Counter by Azumio Inc. <a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/KEs3cb.i[/url]）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2FKEs3cb.i%5B%2Furl%5D%EF%BC%89&d=B9vEvDCwEPmWLQ%2F7k76FykbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=26f8fde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/KEs3cb.i[/url]）</a><br />\n呢個app係影相就知卡路里（雖然唔知準唔準）<br />\n影完就用下面個app計<br />\n2）記錄自己運動同飲食 （[url]薄荷-健康的减肥健身软件 by BOOHEE TECHNOLOGY <a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/xqLsB.i[/url]）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2FxqLsB.i%5B%2Furl%5D%EF%BC%89&d=B9vEvDCwEPmWLQ%2F7k76FykbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bb90b27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/xqLsB.i[/url]）</a><br />\n用用下就會識<br />\n<br />\n用過覺得暫時最好用係呢兩個"},{"pid":"3fc32d472aea345041a435b5c856bdfa0004e53a","tid":349602,"uid":82688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，介唔介意講下用乜方法減<br />\n我諗住每餐份量食少啲，然後又唔食正餐以外既野<br />\n可能再加少少少少運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太懶，其實運動都，唔太激烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" clas